"title": "6703: peace, divine in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6703: peace, divine in ot",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Providing peace for his creation is a characteristic of God. In the OT peace came through adherence to God's will as expressed in his spoken word, covenants and law. The Hebrew word “shalom” means “peace in all its fulness, in every aspect of life”.</p>\n<h2>Peace provided for God's people</h2>\n<h3>Through obedience to God's spoken word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:13-2Kgs5:19\">2KI 5:13–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:21-Job22:22\">JOB 22:21–22:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:8\">PSA 85:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:13\">ISA 54:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:15-Dan10:19\">DAN 10:15–10:19</a></p>\n<h3>Through obedience to God's covenants</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:9\">DEU 29:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:15-Deut30:16\">DEU 30:15–30:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:1-Mal2:6\">MAL 2:1–2:6</a></p>\n<h3>Through obedience to God's laws</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:165\">PSA 119:165</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:3-Lev26:12\">LEV 26:3–26:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1-Deut28:7\">DEU 28:1–28:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:2-2Chr14:7\">2CH 14:2–14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:34-Ps37:38\">PSA 37:34–37:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:17\">PRO 3:13–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:18\">ISA 48:18</a></p>\n<h3>Peace expressed in signs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:13-Gen9:16\">GEN 9:13–9:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:21-Exod13:22\">EXO 13:21–13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:36-Exod40:38\">EXO 40:36–40:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:22-Judg6:24\">JDG 6:22–6:24</a></p>\n<h2>Peace provided for God's nation</h2>\n<h3>Through provision of the land</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:11\">PSA 37:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:13-1Sam7:14\">1SA 7:13–7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:40\">1CH 4:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:3\">PSA 37:3</a></p>\n<h3>Through provision of a holy city</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:20-Isa33:24\">ISA 33:20–33:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:6-Ps122:8\">PSA 122:6–122:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:10-Isa66:13\">ISA 66:10–66:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:16-Zech1:17\">ZEC 1:16–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through provision of a house of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:9\">HAG 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:6-1Chr22:10\">1CH 22:6–22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:24-Ezek37:28\">EZK 37:24–37:28</a></p>\n<h3>Through provision of the law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:18\">ISA 48:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:1-Deut6:3\">DEU 6:1–6:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:15-Deut30:16\">DEU 30:15–30:16</a></p>\n<h2>The benefits of peace</h2>\n<h3>Peace and God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:22-Num6:26\">NUM 6:22–6:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:9\">JOS 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:4\">PSA 23:1–23:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:11\">PSA 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:10-Jer30:11\">JER 30:10–30:11</a></p>\n<h3>Peace in captivity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:7\">JER 29:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:6-Exod1:12\">EXO 1:6–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:1-Jer31:2\">JER 31:1–31:2</a></p>\n<h3>Peace in suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:50\">PSA 119:50</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:4\">ISA 61:1–61:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer34:1-Jer34:5\">JER 34:1–34:5</a></p>\n<h3>Peace in poverty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:30\">ISA 14:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:6-1Sam2:9\">1SA 2:6–2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps68:5-Ps68:10\">PSA 68:5–68:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:1\">PRO 17:1</a></p>\n<h3>Peace with enemies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:7\">PRO 16:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:7-1Chr22:9\">1CH 22:7–22:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:4-Jer29:7\">JER 29:4–29:7</a></p>",
